I Have given ſome hints of cuſtom, but now will handle it more fully. Some Phyſitians deſpiſe cuſtome as a poor inconſiderable thing [vide quoddam theorema] 6. Epidem. 2.26. thinking no indication, or manifeſtation to be taken from cuſtome to change diet, or cure of ſickneſſe. So Theſſalus that vaporing bragadocio made

